{"tid":353725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小店結業】皇仁仔不捨沙茶醬魚蛋 老闆：賺到朋友同回憶","createTime":"2017-08-10T00:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T07:48:23.000Z","uid":37661,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55787c96e0f392330f5788ec370ad6f7e7d4d8ab","tid":353725,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:37:06.000Z","msg":"【小店結業】皇仁仔不捨沙茶醬魚蛋 老闆：賺到朋友同回憶<br />\n<br />\n「煥林粉麵食店」位於銅鑼灣中央圖書館旁邊，直呼其名或者無人識；但一提起沙茶醬魚蛋，相信附近的學生哥、街坊及上班族，一定立即恍然大悟。早前有皇仁學生於faceBook專頁撰文指，該小店將於10月中結業，大嘆可惜。<br />\n<br />\n記者到訪小店，發現檔口均貼上結業字眼，老闆周俊才笑說早前有熟客告訴他faceBook貼文一事，「有幾百個回應，我都很開心，賺不到很多錢，卻賺到很多朋友及美好回憶。」就結業一事，近六十歲的他除感謝大家厚愛，亦當場解釋：「加租是其中一個原因，另一個原因是自己身體不太好，年紀開始大，心臟也不太好，有少許心律不正。」十年以來，老闆與太太、其姊妹，四人日做13小時，每個月只放兩日假，做的是幾蚊生意，賺不多。自調的沙茶醬是小店招牌，用幾款沙茶醬混合、爆鑊後再加蒜蓉煮成，是熟客至愛。雖然今次去意已決，但心底仍希望再回來，他透露未來希望物色到較便宜舖位，看看有無機會重開。<br />\n<br />\n煥林粉麵食店<br />\n地址：銅鑼灣摩頓臺33號<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/08/08/3413325/20170810_sub554new_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F3413325%2F20170810_sub554new_clean_w.mp4&d=G6m4a0XYGbAzLntwRX7pqDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=921d039c\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/08/08/3413325/20170810_sub554new_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502190955_3d94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502190955_3d94.jpg&h=9b95f681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502190956_474d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502190956_474d.jpg&h=f92ea616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502190958_9140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502190958_9140.jpg&h=142e6ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170809/57057212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170809%2F57057212&d=G6m4a0XYGbAzLntwRX7pqDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=e853d975\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170809%2F57057212&h=eb6f55fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170809/57057212</a>"},{"pid":"0ea677946ef601fbfd1b815c4067795287550bad","tid":353725,"uid":4360,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:50:44.000Z","msg":"食過雞蛋仔同格仔餅都好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bb4c4ef1f400b1052dfd7728760a698b2de208","tid":353725,"uid":96858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食過雞蛋仔同格仔餅都好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過沙茶醬真心好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12b25fab16cec41e6af244e3e04e9825af60fb3","tid":353725,"uid":110719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:52:56.000Z","msg":"呢間野出名難食 難忘的味道"},{"pid":"2c44dc5e2fe611d6e430ae36fa98ddd97a6565ed","tid":353725,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:57:11.000Z","msg":"賺到笑啦"},{"pid":"e88bf1fc693f8c3c5ff228b900909c106353df87","tid":353725,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢間野出名難食 難忘的味道</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你食開屎唔慣正常野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af343e83e87c5ecc0e3fa94c546f1b3960f6150","tid":353725,"uid":77092,"